com.personal.foody.web.models

Class SubCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.personal.foody.web.models.SubCategory

  • public class SubCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by danielastamati on 30/01/16. Class to hold restaurant offer information. Such as:
    • subcategory ID
    • subcategory name (ex: pizza)
    • minimum price in EUR
    • minimum price in RON
    • maximum price in RON
    • maximum price in EUR

    WARNING: do not modify the SerializedNames in this class since they correspond to the JSON objects received from the backend. An 1 to 1 correspondence ensures that Gson.fromJson(JsonElement, Class) will work properly when decapsulating JSON data
